data.description:
Welcome to your future oasis! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a testament to comfort and style. Step inside to discover a haven of modern amenities and thoughtful design.

 

Upon entry, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, seamlessly blending spaciousness and functionality. The ceramic tile flooring throughout ensures easy maintenance and adds a touch of elegance to every corner.

 

Entertain with ease in the expansive living area, where natural light floods through new windows, creating an inviting ambiance for gatherings of any size. A formal dining area offers a perfect setting for intimate dinners, while the huge eat-in kitchen beckons culinary adventures with its ample counter space and a large pantry for all your storage needs.

 

Escape to your private retreat in the master suite, boasting comfort and tranquility with its well-appointed en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, home offices, or whatever your heart desires.

 

Outside, a screened-in lanai invites you to unwind and enjoy the Florida sunshine in peace and privacy. And rest assured, a brand-new roof will be installed before closing, ensuring peace of mind for years to come.

 

With a generous 1,745 square feet of living space, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With just a touch of tender loving care, this home will blossom into the perfect sanctuary to call your own. Its solid foundation and array of modern upgrades lay the groundwork for your personal touches and creative vision to shine through, transforming it into the ultimate expression of your lifestyle and taste. Don't miss this opportunity to turn dreams into reality - seize the chance to make this house your home today!
